Titolo: Classic Adventure

Anno: 1982

Descrizione: Classic Adventure, also known as Adventure 1, is a fantasy text-based video game released by Abersoft in 1982.  It was originally released as Adventure 1 on the ZX Spectrum in 1982 before being changed to Classic Adventure in 1984-1985 and re-released on more platforms.Classic Adventure is a remake of the 1976 text adventure game Colossal Cave Adventure.